HIGH-SOLIDS FILTRATION Tackling nasty, high-solids water is what this product does best. Advanced, proven and patented, TEQUATIC™ PLUS Filters operate where traditional filtration technologies typically fail. Whether using this product as a prefilter, primary filter or final filter in your operations, or as an alternative to dissolved air flotation, it can help you turn challenging water into a manageable fluid stream. Learn More.




 

ULTRAFILTRATION It's not kinda-sorta-maybe filtration, it's ultra-filtration—and it excludes particles as small as 0.01 microns. With over 900 installations worldwide, our portfolio of UF products are designed for high productivity, efficiency, exceptional reliability and have a small footprint. Learn More.




 

REVERSE OSMOSIS & NANOFILTRATION Driving technology forward is what we do best. We just happen to do it in reverse. Our RO and NF technologies skip the old-school filters and screens, and bring world-trusted, top-tier technology to your water filtration efforts. Learn More.




 

ION EXCHANGE RESINS Shopping for the right treatment solution? Say hello to the industry’s most complete line of IX resins—featuring a myriad of compositions, structures and sizes. Exchanges always welcome. Learn More.




 

ELECTRODEIONIZATION Ions out—profits in. Our alternative EDI technology has been helping companies like yours achieve high-purity water and high financial returns for years. Learn More.




















