PRODUCT TECHNOLOGIES
We are innovators in purification and separation technologies, setting industry standards for quality and reliability with a comprehensive portfolio of products.










HIGH-SOLIDS FILTRATION
TEQUATIC™ PLUS Filters are self-cleaning and reliable, designed to efficiently remove high solids from problem water without constant plugging, even in the presence of fats, oils and grease.
FIND OUT MORE




ULTRAFILTRATION
A pressure-driven membrane technology that separates particulate matter from soluble components. Membranes reject particulates that are 0.01 microns and larger with the capability to remove bacteria, viruses, colloids, silt and more.
FIND OUT MORE




REVERSE OSMOSIS & NANOFILTRATION
We are recognized as a world leader in RO technology and excel at softening industrial water, demineralizing brackish water, desalinating seawater and more.
FIND OUT MORE




ION EXCHANGE RESINS
We offer one of the industry’s most comprehensive lines of IE resins—handling polymer-based applications as diverse as industrial water softening, ultrapure water production, sweetener purification and more.
FIND OUT MORE




ELECTRODEIONIZATION
Ions out—profits in. Our alternative EDI technology has been helping companies like yours achieve high-purity water and high financial returns for years.
