As Tower Semiconductor LTD (TSEM) Stock Value Rose, Ion Asset Management LTD Has Increased Stake by $4.77 Million, Intl Paper Co (IP) Holder Pinnacle Financial Partners Has Boosted Stake

July 24, 2017 - By Louis Casey

Bart Baum increased its stake in Tower Semiconductor Ltd (TSEM) by 232.09% based on its latest 2016Q4 regulatory filing with the SEC. Ion Asset Management Ltd bought 250,885 shares as the company’s stock rose 11.63% with the market. The hedge fund run by Bart Baum held 358,985 shares of the semiconductors company at the end of 2016Q4, valued at $6.83M, up from 108,100 at the end of the previous reported quarter. Ion Asset Management Ltd who had been investing in Tower Semiconductor Ltd for a number of months, seems to be bullish on the $2.50B market cap company. The stock declined 1.00% or $0.27 reaching $26.78 on the news. About 271,602 shares traded. Tower Semiconductor Ltd. (USA) (NASDAQ:TSEM) has risen 122.17% since July 24, 2016 and is uptrending. It has outperformed by 105.47% the S&P500.







Pinnacle Financial Partners Inc increased its stake in Intl Paper Co (IP) by 90.95% based on its latest 2016Q4 regulatory filing with the SEC. Pinnacle Financial Partners Inc bought 17,666 shares as the company’s stock declined 1.99% while stock markets rallied. The institutional investor held 37,089 shares of the paper company at the end of 2016Q4, valued at $1.97 million, up from 19,423 at the end of the previous reported quarter. Pinnacle Financial Partners Inc who had been investing in Intl Paper Co for a number of months, seems to be bullish on the $23.35B market cap company. The stock rose 0.34% or $0.19 reaching $56.83 per share. About 455,272 shares traded. International Paper Co (NYSE:IP) has risen 26.95% since July 24, 2016 and is uptrending. It has outperformed by 10.25% the S&P500.
Another recent and important Tower Semiconductor Ltd. (USA) (NASDAQ:TSEM) news was published by Benzinga.com which published an article titled: “Tower Semiconductor Reaches January 2011 Levels After Q4 Beat” on February 13, 2017.
Among 4 analysts covering TowerJazz (NASDAQ:TSEM), 4 have Buy rating, 0 Sell and 0 Hold. Therefore 100% are positive. TowerJazz had 7 analyst reports since August 6, 2015 according to SRatingsIntel. Oppenheimer initiated Tower Semiconductor Ltd. (USA) (NASDAQ:TSEM) on Tuesday, December 15 with “Outperform” rating. Needham maintained the stock with “Buy” rating in Wednesday, June 21 report. The rating was maintained by Chardan Capital Markets with “Buy” on Thursday, August 6. As per Friday, January 22, the company rating was initiated by Needham. Drexel Hamilton initiated Tower Semiconductor Ltd. (USA) (NASDAQ:TSEM) on Tuesday, October 20 with “Buy” rating. The stock of Tower Semiconductor Ltd. (USA) (NASDAQ:TSEM) has “Buy” rating given on Friday, June 9 by Needham.
Investors sentiment decreased to 0.97 in 2016 Q4. Its down 0.26, from 1.23 in 2016Q3. It dived, as 64 investors sold IP shares while 255 reduced holdings. 75 funds opened positions while 234 raised stakes. 332.47 million shares or 2.22% more from 325.25 million shares in 2016Q3 were reported. Baker Ellis Asset Mgmt Lc has invested 1.11% in International Paper Co (NYSE:IP). First Advisors Limited Partnership has 0.08% invested in International Paper Co (NYSE:IP). Cullinan stated it has 5,471 shares. Two Sigma Ltd reported 5,706 shares or 0.1% of all its holdings. Asset One Limited stated it has 0.1% in International Paper Co (NYSE:IP). Atria Investments Ltd Liability Corporation accumulated 31,967 shares or 0.13% of the stock. Clearbridge Invests Ltd Limited Liability Company has 6.14 million shares. Proshare Advsr Limited Com holds 42,648 shares. 5,574 were reported by Rfg Advisory Gp Limited Liability. 36,334 were reported by Capstone Asset Mgmt. Iridian Asset Mgmt Lc Ct invested in 0.74% or 1.50M shares. Livingston Group Inc Asset Mngmt (Operating As Southport Capital Management) has invested 0.41% in International Paper Co (NYSE:IP). Stratos Wealth Ptnrs Limited invested in 0.03% or 10,026 shares. Oakbrook Invs Ltd Liability owns 0.07% invested in International Paper Co (NYSE:IP) for 21,000 shares. Minnesota-based Us Natl Bank De has invested 0.08% in International Paper Co (NYSE:IP).
Among 13 analysts covering International Paper Company (NYSE:IP), 5 have Buy rating, 2 Sell and 6 Hold. Therefore 38% are positive. International Paper Company had 44 analyst reports since August 4, 2015 according to SRatingsIntel. As per Wednesday, July 19, the company rating was maintained by RBC Capital Markets. The firm earned “Hold” rating on Thursday, September 17 by Deutsche Bank. The firm earned “Neutral” rating on Tuesday, August 2 by Citigroup. RBC Capital Markets upgraded International Paper Co (NYSE:IP) rating on Wednesday, April 19. RBC Capital Markets has “Outperform” rating and $56 target. The firm has “Outperform” rating by BMO Capital Markets given on Wednesday, January 25. On Tuesday, July 11 the stock rating was maintained by KeyBanc Capital Markets with “Hold”. The stock of International Paper Co (NYSE:IP) has “Buy” rating given on Thursday, July 13 by Goldman Sachs. The firm earned “Buy” rating on Monday, May 29 by RBC Capital Markets. On Tuesday, August 25 the stock rating was upgraded by Buckingham Research to “Neutral”. RBC Capital Markets downgraded International Paper Co (NYSE:IP) on Monday, April 25 to “Sector Perform” rating.
Pinnacle Financial Partners Inc, which manages about $462.51 million US Long portfolio, decreased its stake in Berkshire Hathaway Inc Del (BRKB) by 1,931 shares to 2,802 shares, valued at $457,000 in 2016Q4, according to the filing. It also reduced its holding in Unitedhealth Group Inc (NYSE:UNH) by 2,350 shares in the quarter, leaving it with 40,013 shares, and cut its stake in Regions Finl Corp New (NYSE:RF). 


