					            About Ion Exchange (India) Ltd.Ion Exchange (India) Ltd., incorporated in the year 1964, is a Small Cap company (having a market cap of ₹ 867.02 Cr.) operating in Engineering sector. Ion Exchange (India) Ltd. key Products/Revenue Segments include Water Treatment Plants which contributed ₹ 318.36 Cr to Sales Value (39.79 % of Total Sales), Chemical Additives which contributed ₹ 156.56 Cr to Sales Value (19.56 % of Total Sales), Resins Ion Exchange which contributed ₹ 155.16 Cr to Sales Value (19.39 % of Total Sales), Sale of services which contributed ₹ 89.67 Cr to Sales Value (11.20 % of Total Sales), Consumer Family Products which contributed ₹ 66.22 Cr to Sales Value (8.27 % of Total Sales), Others which contributed ₹ 6.52 Cr to Sales Value (0.81 % of Total Sales), Spares And Others which contributed ₹ 4.99 Cr to Sales Value (0.62 % of Total Sales), Scrap which contributed ₹ 2.08 Cr to Sales Value (0.25 % of Total Sales), Other Operating Revenue which contributed ₹ .51 Cr to Sales Value (0.06 % of Total Sales)for the year ending 31-Mar-2016.For the quarter ended 30-06-2017, the company has reported a  Standalone sales of ₹ 208.05 Cr., down -39.97 from last quarter Sales of ₹ 346.58 Cr. and up 9.56 from last year same quarter Sales of ₹ 189.90 Cr. Company has reported net profit after tax of ₹ 7.29 Cr. in latest quarter.The company’s top management includes Dr.V N Gupchup, Mr.Aankur Patni, Mr.Abhiram Seth, Mr.Dinesh Sharma, Mr.M P Patni, Mr.P Sampathkumar, Mr.Rajesh Sharma, Mr.Shishir Tamotia, Mr.T M M Nambiar, Mrs.K J Udeshi. Company has BSR & Co. LLP as its auditors. As on 30-06-2017, the company has a total of 14,666,659 shares outstanding.View Details:Chairman's SpeechCompany HistoryDirectors ReportBackground informationCompany ManagementListing InformationFinished ProductsBoard MeetingsAGM/EGMClose XAlertWatchlistPortfolioCurrent Price: 2389.88Lower LimitUpper LimitSet AlertTo continue receiving alerts, please enter your email id below:Enter e